Best Global Universities for Arts and Humanities

The broad field of arts and humanities deals with the study of human history and expression. Among the subjects included in this discipline are archaeology; language and linguistics; and performing arts. These are the world's top universities for arts and humanities. Read the methodology »

To unlock more data and access tools to help you get into your dream school, sign up for the U.S. News College Compass!

Summary

Here are the best global universities for arts and humanities

  1. University of Oxford
  2. Harvard University
  3. University of Cambridge
  4. University College London
  5. Yale University
  6. New York University
  7. University of Edinburgh
  8. Stanford University
